You walk into the room and are shocked to be staring at yourself across the distance. Every surface around you is smooth and mirrored. There are two pillars in the corners of the room, one white, one black, and a rope coiled between the two. One column is black, the other white. There is a door to the North.

#ROOM_STATE_1#

Mirrored room with two pillars, one white, one black, and a door to the North.

#ROOM_STATE_2#

Once the pillars are tied, you hear a grinding sound as the pillars slide together into the center of the room.